{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 7",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-608124842226483972 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=608106698237805466&sectionId=608124842226483972)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDRU4-RkAZ_text","label":"ggDRU4-RkAZ_text","default":"<p>The Transformation That Stunned Everyone</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrmzMKhVj3_text","label":"ggrmzMKhVj3_text","default":"<p>Sarah wore the Tavio pack every night. The results followed a pattern Gary would later see repeated across dozens of people:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf2dTxWXNL_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggf2dTxWXNL_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPCC13Sf8y_text","label":"ggPCC13Sf8y_text","default":"<p><strong>Days 1-3:</strong> Increased gurgling and abdominal activity. \"Things are moving in there,\" Sarah said. \"For the first time in years, something is actually happening.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghKcIyDhhV_text","label":"gghKcIyDhhV_text","default":"<p><strong>Days 4-7:</strong> First reduction in afternoon bloating. Made it to 4 PM without unbuttoning her pants. Bathroom activity increased.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbVSCGwpjf_text","label":"ggbVSCGwpjf_text","default":"<p><strong>Days 8-10: </strong>The morning that changed everything. Rope-like biofilm masses finally releasing. Years of buildup breaking apart. Sarah whispered: \"That was inside me this whole time. And every doctor said I was fine.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQIon4Nzge_text","label":"ggQIon4Nzge_text","default":"<p><strong>Days 11-14:</strong> Bloating dropped dramatically. Could button her jeans all day. Wore a fitted top to work for the first time in two years.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPsiEVJH4_text","label":"ggQPsiEVJH4_text","default":"<p><strong>Days 15-18:</strong> The 3 AM wake-ups stopped. Sarah slept through the night for the first time in two years. Gary woke at 6 AM and she was still sleeping. He lay there in silence — not because he couldn't sleep, but because he couldn't believe she finally could.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAoatJDdwk_text","label":"ggAoatJDdwk_text","default":"<p><strong>Days 19-21:</strong> Sarah ate pasta, bread, and dessert for dinner. Woke up flat. No bloating. No pain. She cried at the breakfast table. Happy tears.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1LoQ2bACh_text","label":"gg1LoQ2bACh_text","default":"<p><strong>Day 35: </strong>Follow-up with her gastroenterologist. \"Your symptoms are completely resolved. What did you do?\" Sarah told him about the biofilm and the castor oil pack. He wrote \"alternative treatment\" in her file and moved on.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFh_9PDdnd_text","label":"ggFh_9PDdnd_text","default":"<p><i>\"Two years. Seven medications. Twenty-three thousand dollars. And he wrote 'alternative treatment' and didn't even ask what it was.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0odANFluB_text","label":"gg0odANFluB_text","default":"<p>The Neighborhood That Woke Up</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU_0e1Z39C_text","label":"ggU_0e1Z39C_text","default":"<p>Word spread the way it always does — one stunned conversation at a time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglF6C3to9t_text","label":"gglF6C3to9t_text","default":"<p><i>\"Started the pack on a Monday. By Friday, the bloating was less. By week three, I'd stopped two of my three IBS medications. My doctor is confused. I don't care.\" —</i> Jen M., neighbor</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKdu0dGUeO_text","label":"ggKdu0dGUeO_text","default":"<p><i>\"Three weeks with the pack. We went to a steakhouse for our anniversary. Full meal. Steak, sides, bread, dessert. No bloating. No bathroom emergency. She ordered dessert and I nearly cried watching her eat without fear.\" — </i>Tom R., Austin, TX</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggu2IPWT2Cs_text","label":"ggu2IPWT2Cs_text","default":"<p><i>\"The 3 AM wake-ups stopped by week two. I feel ten years younger.\" — </i>Mike D., Austin, TX</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0C-GVpkzJ_text","label":"gg0C-GVpkzJ_text","default":"<p><i>\"Nothing worked. Every protocol. Every supplement. Every diet. Two weeks with the pack and I ate bread for the first time in two years. I wept into a dinner roll and I'm not ashamed of it.\" — </i>Linda K., Austin, TX</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQYOM9PUXO_text","label":"ggQYOM9PUXO_text","default":"<p>Within three months, seventeen families in Gary and Sarah's circle were using the pack nightly. The pattern was unmistakable:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdsRwNtzlP_text","label":"ggdsRwNtzlP_text","default":"<p>✅ Week 1: Increased gut activity, mobilization beginning</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfmy2ndDsF_text","label":"ggfmy2ndDsF_text","default":"<p>✅ Week 2: Bloating reduction — most could button pants all day</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdC47NMrXG_text","label":"ggdC47NMrXG_text","default":"<p>✅ Week 2-3: 3 AM wake-ups stopped</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGoo4SQSb1_text","label":"ggGoo4SQSb1_text","default":"<p>✅ Week 3-4: Biofilm expulsion — visible mucus-like strands passing</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_Emy7Z-2p_text","label":"gg_Emy7Z-2p_text","default":"<p>✅ Month 2: Complete resolution of chronic bloating, normalized sleep</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6fzPBnYgu_text","label":"gg6fzPBnYgu_text","default":"<p>The local pharmacy reported a noticeable decline in IBS medication refills. Sarah's gastroenterologist noted several patients with \"spontaneous improvement.\" He didn't investigate further.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3aLqH4LfR_text","label":"gg3aLqH4LfR_text","default":"<p>The Numbers That Should Make You Angry</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMnGs6WadP_text","label":"ggMnGs6WadP_text","default":"<p>The IBS medication market generates $1.8 billion annually. Gut health supplements: $3.2 billion. Gastroenterology visits: $4.7 billion. Colonoscopies: $14.7 billion.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCOfZCYydj_text","label":"ggCOfZCYydj_text","default":"<p><strong>The chronic gut symptom management industry: over </strong><span style=\"color:#B22121;\"><strong>$24 billion a year.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQRcG27qCj_text","label":"ggQRcG27qCj_text","default":"<p>Every one of those dollars depends on people managing symptoms instead of addressing the root cause.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5mNwEuw-0_text","label":"gg5mNwEuw-0_text","default":"<p>A reusable castor oil pack that costs $44 and works while you sleep doesn't generate gastroenterology visits. Doesn't sell monthly prescriptions. Doesn't create lifelong supplement customers.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYZhbryET6_text","label":"ggYZhbryET6_text","default":"<p><i>\"They don't want you to fix it. They want you to manage it. Forever. At four hundred dollars a month.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXptPLGM0y_text","label":"ggXptPLGM0y_text","default":"<p>What Sarah Says Now</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9qmIL2AYJ_text","label":"gg9qmIL2AYJ_text","default":"<p>Sarah Whitfield is 47 now. She runs her team again. Trains for a 10K. Eats whatever she wants — pasta, bread, dessert — without unbuttoning her pants or mapping the nearest bathroom.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3zUFh2joK_text","label":"gg3zUFh2joK_text","default":"<p>She sleeps through the night. Every night. She still wears her Tavio pack to bed. Sixty seconds to put on. Takes it off in the morning.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd-Js-VqnT_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggd-Js-VqnT_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSWo3WL1yx_text","label":"ggSWo3WL1yx_text","default":"<p><i>\"I'm not the bloated, exhausted zombie anymore. I'm not the woman afraid to eat, afraid to wear fitted clothes, afraid something was wrong with her that nobody could find. I'm me again. For the first time in years.\" — </i>Sarah Whitfield</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaNyI4E_lW_text","label":"ggaNyI4E_lW_text","default":"<p>Over 85% of Americans are carrying parasites right now. Most will never be tested. Their doctors will call it IBS, hormones, stress, anxiety. They'll prescribe pills for every symptom and never once ask why they're all happening at the same time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3G5Ay2cup_text","label":"gg3G5Ay2cup_text","default":"<p>If you or someone you love is living with bloating that never goes away, 3 AM wake-ups, and an \"IBS\" diagnosis that leads nowhere — consider this:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG89c282X-_text","label":"ggG89c282X-_text","default":"<p>It's not IBS. It's parasites hiding behind biofilm in the intestinal wall. No pill can reach them there. They need to be reached transdermally. Through the skin. With sustained compression and body heat. Overnight.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg26ZnNME5g_text","label":"gg26ZnNME5g_text","default":"<p>That's what the pack does. That's all it does. And it's enough.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEk-8-bbGq_text","label":"ggEk-8-bbGq_text","default":"<p>Sarah's proof. Jen's proof. Tom's wife is proof. Mike's proof. Linda's proof.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggawLGC8Zq__text","label":"ggawLGC8Zq__text","default":"<p>Three weeks from now, you could be proof too.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4CD9gHRfm_label","label":"gg4CD9gHRfm_label","default":"<p>CLAIM YOUR TAVIO PACK NOW — WHILE STILL AVAILABLE</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3NkJSgS9M_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg3NkJSgS9M_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOY3aNyV3p_text","labe